    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has served me so well\u2014super reliable and a total blast to drive! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it's just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great, this is the one for you. Drop me a message, I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
