    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example is paired with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering a purely analog driving experience. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing performance. Suspension components remain tight, featuring refreshed bushings and a limited-slip differential that maintains excellent lockup. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the powertrain remains a testament to BMW M engineering, delivering linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key driver for the purist who prioritizes mechanical integrity and handling dynamics.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
