    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss luster, showing only minor stone chips on the hood and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014evidence of careful but consistent use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats are firm and free of cracks, and the dashboard remains pristine without any sun fading. Every feature, from the heated seats to the navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the car is mechanically sound with a documented service history, including a recent fluid flush and new tires installed just 3,000 miles ago. It starts reliably, idles quietly, and delivers a smooth, confident ride. This is an honest, solid car for a buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean presentation.",
      "price": 31500.0,
