    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you\u2019re getting a great vehicle at a really fair price. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
