    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and benefits from a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and recent shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustments. The drivetrain consists of a crisp Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission delivering power to a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis handles high lateral G-loads with precision. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals and powertrain cooling systems are in top-tier operational order.",
